snippet.textDisplay:
Some songs are new to you but by the end of it you are so engrossed that you seem to hold various co-incidences with the song and it becomes a part of you. This song is definitely one of them! It relives you, it soothes you and it makes you aware of larger truths! Probably the best qawwali with the base creating the right aura which wouldnt be present during Nusratjis times. Shiraz In no time has become a favourite and Rafakat ji with his voice takes the song to a different high altogether! Thankyou Coke studio for this one ! Probably the pick of this season. Coke studio gets better with each season! 
Much love from india, already waiting for the next season!
